result.execSummary:
The defendant Rolando Jimenez Jr. was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case.

  • Bail Jumping-Misdemeanor, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
  • Bail-Jumping-Misdemeanor, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
  • Bail Jumping Misdemeanor, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
  • Rock County Ordinance - Disorderly Conduct [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse Incident]. This is not a criminal offense and results only in a money penalty for this offense.
